dc_title_s: County and municipality map of New Jersey: political boundaries revised to June 30, 1956
dc_description_s: New Jersey. Department of Conservation and Economic Development. Division of Planning and Development. Atlas Sheet no. 39 (1956) (County/municipality) New Jersey Geological Survey. Political boundries revised to June 30, l956. n upper margin: Sheet 39. From original survey, based on triangulation of the U.S. Coast and Geodetic Survey; C. C. Vermeule, Topographer. The shore lines of tidal waters are mainly from the U. S. C. & G. Survey. Boundary lines revised by R. G. Blanchard, Topographic Engineer.
dc_publisher_s: Trenton, N.J. : New Jersey Geological Survey, 1956.
